From 4Media Software Studio: 

4Media Ringtone Maker can make ringtones from just about any popular video (even HD) and music format including AVI, MPEG, WMV, DivX, MP4, H.264/AVC, AVCHD, MKV, RM, MOV, XviD, 3GP, WMA, WAV, RA, M4A, MP3 and so on to MP3, WAV, M4R, AMR, M4A or OGG format, turning your beloved songs or video soundtracks into ringtones for your iPhone, BlackBerry, Google phone, Windows Mobile, Nokia, Motorola, Sony Ericsson or other mobile phones. Key features: 1.Supports numerous of audio formats (including MP3, WMA, WAV, RA, M4A, AAC, AC3, OGG and so on) as the input, and converts them into MP3, WAV, M4R, AMR, M4A or OGG format as your ringtones. 2.Make ringtones in MP3, WAV, M4R, AMR, M4A or OGG audio format from video formats including AVI, MPEG, WMV, DivX, MP4, H.264/AVC, AVCHD, MKV, RM, MOV, XviD, 3GP. 3.Supported devices include the iPhone (iPhone 1st generation, iPhone 3G, iPhone 3GS), Google phones, BlackBerry, Windows Mobile devices, amongst many other mobile phone brands and models. 4.Add fade-in and fade-out effects to your ringtones. 5.Extract the segment you want from a media file and convert it to the ringtone in the format you want. 6.Check the fading effects, volume and clipped segment with the built-in media player before conversion. 7.Adjust the bit rate/sample rate/audio channel and set the output format before conversion. 8.Import files to be converted into ringtones easily using drag and drop; adjust the ringtone volume; rename the ringtone at will. 9.Interface available in English, German, Spanish, French, Japanese and Chinese.

